(4228, 1, '2016-01-26 02:44:26', '2016-01-26 02:44:26', 'I hate this transitional period where the weather constantly changes and you never know what coat to take with you for the day. I think I may have to hit Zara again today to mix up my summer to fall jacket collection.\n\nOn a more exciting note, I’m off to Mallorca on Friday for 10 days whoop. I’m so excited to be able to properly say good bye to summer and enjoy these last moments of tanning. We have a villa in Calvia with a gorgeous pool and I can’t wait to show you on Instagram, so please follow me if you aren’t already. I will be taking it down a notch with blogging but I do have a few exciting things planned whilst out there that I’m sure you will love.\n\n<img class="size-medium wp-image-4225 alignright" src="http://wp.rivertheme.com/ri-everest/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/p2h1-300x203.jpg" alt="p2h1" width="300" height="203" />\n\nBack to my fashion post, this week I decided to share this 70’s inspired accessible street style which I styled with these gorgeous red snake skin boots with a block heel that I got from Asos in the style of Maison Margilla a couple of weeks ago but I can’t seem to find them on their website any longer which is rather odd.', 'Stress style fashion collection 2016', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'stress-style-fashion-collection-2016', '', '', '2016-01-26 02:44:26', '2016-01-26 02:44:26', '', 0, 'http://wp.rivertheme.com/ri-everest/?p=4228', 0, 'post', '', 0),
